parameters:
\SE[4]Lunaroa? \SE[3]There's something I want to ask you, can you
spare a little time?
\SE[2]No response, huh? I wonder if she's gone somewhere.
\SE[4]Ah, I wonder if she's in Laura's room...?

\SE[4]Laura? \. Is Lunaroa over there? \!\SE[3]I want to borrow
her for a little bit.

\SE[14]Now, give up, Laura...! \SE[43]Today, I absolutely won't
let you escape...! \SE[74]I can't bear it anymore, let's be
together!!

\SE[95]You said the same thing yesterday too! \SE[50]Ever since
you grew a thing, we've been doing it almost every day. I've been
trying various things like taking baths and setting the mood
too...!

\SE[31]You don't have to worry about things like taking a bath.
\SE[60]I don't really pay attention to such trivial matters.
[2]Besides, I can feel the condensed Laura, so it's actually
good.

\SE[33]I don't like it!! \!\SE[95]I want to show you a more
beautiful side of me...!

\SE[74]...I'm doing something pointless again. \. It's
troublesome to get involved, \. Maybe I should start over...

\SE[73]You're such an disobedient child...! \!\SE[74]But,
resistance is futile against this magic...!!

\SE[66]Hehe... Look, see? Your beloved thing.... \. You've become
completely addicted to it, haven't you? \!\SE[70]I'll make you
surrender that stubborn attitude with pleasure...!

\SE[100]Ku...!! \!\SE[102]I absolutely won't lose to a thing like
that...! \!\SE[5]...Huh?
\SE[93]Is it just me, or do I not have a thing like that...?

\SE[4]Ah, I did it...! \!\SE[23]I got carried away and ended up
fully manifesting the futanari...!

\SE[57]Is this the time for Futanari Fencing...? \SE[58]If it has
come to this... there's only that left.

\SE[12]The rules are simple. \!\SE[43]We clash against each other
like 'spears' and the first one to be defeated loses.
\!\SE[72]The loser accepts the winner and becomes the 'female'.

\SE[61]Will you show me your cool side, Laura? \. Or are you
afraid of losing?

\SE[38]I'm not afraid of defeat.... I want to show you my cool
side too...!! \SM[nod]\SE[102]That's why I will never run away!

\SE[15]That's what makes you my beloved...! \SM[nod]\SE[71]Now,
let's go to the bed...!!
\SM[nod]\SE[97]Yeah, I absolutely won't lose or anything...!!

\SE[116]W-Wait a minute...! \SE[33]I, already...!? Why so
soon...!?

\SE[15]Hehe... You fell into my trap, didn't you? \SE[66]I've
increased the sensitivity of your 'penis' by 'three times'. Even
the slightest breeze will make you 'ejaculate'!

\SE[109]Three times...!? \. Then there's no chance of winning
from the start!?

\SE[16]It's too late to realize now. \. Just give up and become a
'female'...!! \!\SE[74]This is your weak spot...\. Look...\.
Look!!
\SE[33]Ah...! I knew it, I couldn't win...!!
Finally... it's almost time, right? I wonder if you're ready...?
